) (
<figureCitation id="1334D0F6FFFBA4573E0000CAF0F8F875" box="[1358,1428,2005,2026]" captionStart="FIGURES 20 – 22" captionStartId="17.[151,264,1912,1935]" captionText="FIGURES 20 – 22. Hercostomus albicoxa sp. nov., holotype. (20) habitus; (21) head; (22) hypopygium." pageId="18" pageNumber="129">Fig. 20</figureCitation>
)
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB0CC73FFFAA4563BD90788F0FAFF78" blockId="19.[151,1436,151,231]" pageId="19" pageNumber="130">
<keyLead id="30FE6F46FFFAA4563BD90788F0FAFF78" pageId="19" pageNumber="130">
- All coxae entirely whitish yellow. Postpedicel (
