<figureCitation id="1334D0F6FFFAA456391807AAF7F0FF55" box="[598,668,181,202]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 25" captionStartId="18.[151,264,1525,1548]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1499]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[151,1436,193,1504]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 25. Hercostomus convergens, holotype. (23) habitus; (24) head; (25) hypopygium." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/376042/files/figure.png" pageId="19" pageNumber="130">Fig. 25</figureCitation>
